column2: IDEA-208067: Fix memory leak via InlayModelImpl$AfterLineEndElementTree

column3:
AfterLineEndElementTrees register themselves as document listeners in
their constructor, but the disposal call in InlayModelImpl which removes
this listener was omitted.
Patch has been pushed to master. It will also be merged into 191 branch.

Sorry forgot to set 'Author' field, so the commit doesn't have your name in it :(
(We apply pull requests manually in our repository).
